{"title":"Inmunocompromiso y Aparato Digestivo","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/General/Inmunocompromiso y Aparato Digestivo-2024-1.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Inmunocompromiso y\\NAparato Digestivo","guid":"vN3dxpQ5_A7XDrZ5Iv1jkA","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Introducción","guid":"","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"• Aumento de trastornos GI mediados por SI.","guid":"HZ6ox8voHMoDVWZUz4b2Zw","children":[]},{"id":"3","parent":"1","text":"• Inmunodeficiencias (ID) primarias y adquiridas → manifestaciones GI.","guid":"YF4QH7krGY1c8AJTpGAg4g","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"1","text":"• Inmunosupresión secundaria o adquirida ↔ terapias farmacológicas.","guid":"hkA1WTQWoiNeRMW8ByzGag","children":[]},{"id":"5","parent":"1","text":"• Trasplantes de órganos sólidos (300/año en Chile).","guid":"kgKH0cpb3Z4b4mMHyoLWqA","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"1","text":"• Nuevas terapias inmunomoduladoras (10%-20% pop.).","guid":"E8Xig7C2I0o1F-hZSojjOA","children":[]},{"id":"7","parent":"1","text":"• Antineoplásicos.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"8","parent":"1","text":"• ID primarias en adultos: SIgAD, CVID.","guid":"cZsxY4U2go0_xCypBosdtQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"9","parent":"0","text":"Concepto de Inmunosupresión y\\NFisiopatología del SI y Aparato Digestivo","guid":"4y_Hgbl8sSex0_sqy6COaA","children":[{"id":"10","parent":"9","text":"• SGI = gran superficie presentadora de Ag.","guid":"isojoVXdFaL9fgj6PxhqGQ","children":[]},{"id":"11","parent":"9","text":"• Modificación de respuesta ↔ estructuras adyacentes (esfínter), procesos digestivos\\N(ácidos, sales biliares, enzimas pancreáticas), pH, tipo de alimento, nutrientes.","guid":"nSW5APs7sCjoh5f6sMhRfg","children":[]},{"id":"12","parent":"9","text":"• Digestión y absorción → moléculas simples → atraviesan pared GI → estimulación local y a distancia ↔ complejo Ag/Ac.","guid":"KnoYTCEe-ptW01SUFbme9A","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"9","text":"• Alteración de estos procesos → síndromes que comprometen RI ↔ sistema digestivo.","guid":"EP8q4lgraFjJa5kPxqHt9w","children":[]}]},{"id":"14","parent":"0","text":"Concepto de Microbioma e\\NInmunosupresión","guid":"","children":[{"id":"15","parent":"14","text":"• TGI humano ↔ red diversa de microorganismos = microbiota.","guid":"-Ke_1-asqq2D6Hiabkv7pQ","children":[]},{"id":"16","parent":"14","text":"• Papel importante en salud y enfermedad.","guid":"dy51rxFf3GA7kX_wqhMGmg","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"14","text":"• SI adaptado ↔ trabajo conjunto con microbiota.","guid":"qZDO8NX5rS2NW-Hh9o8dyQ","children":[]},{"id":"18","parent":"14","text":"• Manipulación de microbiota → prevenir enfermedades.","guid":"ZKKY0GpxMrt_u1lmvGcKIQ","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"14","text":"• Alteración por antibióticos/inmunosupresores → vulnerabilidad ↔ enfermedades nosocomiales.","guid":"kHLPVdpOplYX2wR8C7uJ4g","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"14","text":"• Microbiota:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"21","parent":"20","text":"• Bacteroidetes, Firmicutes, Actinobacteria, Proteobacteria.","guid":"r_hAbBVnqgzGwxXrgMLsxQ","children":[]},{"id":"22","parent":"20","text":"• Bacteroidetes = 90% densidad.","guid":"KyErWUmbwmdLpTiKYPssyA","children":[]},{"id":"23","parent":"20","text":"• Cambios ↔ distribución anatómica → absorción de nutrientes, modificación de pH, producción de mucus, presentación de Ag a nivel celular.","guid":"DKCdbEuP5VOyeu09fbvhYg","children":[]},{"id":"24","parent":"20","text":"• Desregulación ↔ cambios en microbioma (ej.: antibióticos, inmunosupresores).","guid":"4vzZw9UP0fA-3uZPLkOuCQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"25","parent":"0","text":"Tipos de\\NInmunosupresión","guid":"","children":[{"id":"26","parent":"25","text":"Primarias","guid":"","children":[{"id":"27","parent":"26","text":"• Déficit selectivo de IgA","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"26","text":"• Inmunodeficiencia común variable","guid":"ZzxfCVBKiAyzQjREczPMoQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"29","parent":"25","text":"Adquiridas","guid":"","children":[{"id":"30","parent":"29","text":"• Secundaria\\Na fármacos:","guid":"lYf5cPbgRJTH2sBhb6PoaQ","children":[{"id":"31","parent":"30","text":"• Quimioterapia/radioterapia/corticoides","guid":"IRJL1ha3iPGRSffjO5VFAw","children":[]},{"id":"32","parent":"30","text":"• Biológicos/inmunosupresión/trasplante","guid":"nHfyYzMr2MCMUrDnLyFzUw","children":[]}]},{"id":"33","parent":"29","text":"• Infecciosas:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"34","parent":"33","text":"• HIV (inmunodeficiencia adquirida)","guid":"HzYETCl_x5QFr_6ivGtknQ","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"33","text":"• No VIH (micobacterias, estreptococos, cándida, parasitosis, chagas, VHB, VHC)","guid":"SeD3oC5MWFVHSUWGP1b5Mw","children":[]}]},{"id":"36","parent":"29","text":"• Metabólicas:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"37","parent":"36","text":"• Sd. Malabsorción","guid":"9f40M-pnES0HiqgYR9Ccgg","children":[]},{"id":"38","parent":"36","text":"• Déficit de oligoelementos","guid":"bHqRNrA-K0W-u44iQxKD4w","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"36","text":"• DM2","guid":"Npsyercr3RByUmwbENn6zw","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"36","text":"• Enfermedades renales","guid":"dL2uLhakkj7bSZkInDESUg","children":[]},{"id":"41","parent":"36","text":"• Enteropatía perdedora de proteínas","guid":"Z0w8izf-EQZo8FEt0VcvjQ","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"42","parent":"0","text":"Inmunodeficiencia\\NPrimaria","guid":"","children":[{"id":"43","parent":"42","text":"Inmunodeficiencia\\NCongénita","guid":"","children":[{"id":"44","parent":"43","text":"I. Deficiencia Selectiva de\\NInmunoglobulina A (SIgAD)","guid":"6HQ4eqvCyLfpkb-svsAsow","children":[{"id":"45","parent":"44","text":"• IgA: >70% de Ig totales en el cuerpo.","guid":"CGqOfsiNQIzqk8yPtw2rcQ","children":[]},{"id":"46","parent":"44","text":"• Baja concentración en suero ↔ secreciones mucosas (nasal, pulmonar, saliva, lágrimas, leche materna, secreciones urogenitales e intestinales).","guid":"Mw2y2aOhSkgdcB3Nqd4nJQ","children":[]},{"id":"47","parent":"44","text":"• Función: recubrimiento de microorganismos → prevención de fijación y penetración de patógenos.","guid":"UgVlh4bLWXpnI9Sd9QrMEA","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"44","text":"• SIgAD:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"49","parent":"48","text":"• ID primaria más común.","guid":"UGzk3L1gIJ1k3PaGpBUgOg","children":[]},{"id":"50","parent":"48","text":"• Definición: ausencia parcial/total de IgA en suero (<0,07 g/L) en >4 años.","guid":"TQiB3lJq7OrZCjH_ggng5Q","children":[]},{"id":"51","parent":"48","text":"• Cifras normales en otras Ig.","guid":"4zorGjKKHq0m32GAEN3F8A","children":[]}]},{"id":"52","parent":"44","text":"• Etiología:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"53","parent":"52","text":"• Susceptibilidad genética no bien definida.","guid":"CbLPOnSjkX6ERL_u7YUgpQ","children":[]},{"id":"54","parent":"52","text":"• Herencia: autosómica dominante/recesiva en algunas familias.","guid":"nLZDhOSPoZd3Rip63Ko0SQ","children":[]},{"id":"55","parent":"52","text":"• Casos esporádicos comunes.","guid":"s2oE-vKETHHPVBx9nOSd0Q","children":[]},{"id":"56","parent":"52","text":"• Asociación: haplotipos HLA (HLA-A1, B8, DR3).","guid":"p2fnKLIIodhDS9pi6E9VQQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"57","parent":"44","text":"• Clínica:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"58","parent":"57","text":"• Mayoría asintomática.","guid":"CzTcvC0mNXQIKajh-qm9Gg","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"57","text":"• Posible compensación por otras Ig (ej.: IgG).","guid":"E47eKGHhWBsTGlP_gM-3uA","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"57","text":"• Mayor riesgo de infecciones (ej.: H. pylori, Giardia lamblia).","guid":"XNnO8yByEJ_9_0ZAcstMBg","children":[]},{"id":"61","parent":"57","text":"• Autoinmunidad: mayor riesgo de enfermedad atópica.","guid":"ScVEJvNT4Th6j4Bd3QesDA","children":[]},{"id":"62","parent":"57","text":"• Enfermedades autoinmunes prevalentes: lupus, enfermedad celíaca, enfermedad inflamatoria intestinal.","guid":"0atB6c1waGbF6iCyM74mSA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"63","parent":"43","text":"II. Inmunodeficiencia\\NComún Variable (IDCV)","guid":"T38EemkVajyx0QXNU-ftrw","children":[{"id":"64","parent":"63","text":"• IDCV:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"65","parent":"64","text":"• Trastorno sintomático más común en adultos con ID primarias.","guid":"fM_pxrcGnZYekpqLAxytIA","children":[]},{"id":"66","parent":"64","text":"• Hipogammaglobulinemia notable (sello distintivo).","guid":"p25RedqGgrHqYYCyFRo9Hg","children":[]}]},{"id":"67","parent":"63","text":"• Clínica:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"68","parent":"67","text":"• Heterogénea y variable.","guid":"N2hr5r8ZUJgfojDvNwACXw","children":[]},{"id":"69","parent":"67","text":"• Bajo número de células plasmáticas y niveles disminuidos de Ig.","guid":"YSDN-T1jOgjLBCCAcvrhjA","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"67","text":"• Infecciones: bacterias en tractos respiratorio y GI.","guid":"vRftlX6mfiAhMnF8aGCoLQ","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"67","text":"• Trastornos autoinmunes a pesar de ID.","guid":"F8MGQR9dLONoK6d7NLkMeA","children":[]},{"id":"72","parent":"67","text":"• Riesgos: neoplasias (especialmente digestivas y hematológicas).","guid":"zLgLuW-TWNX_HCb4LKrlHw","children":[]}]},{"id":"73","parent":"63","text":"• Manifestaciones\\NGI:","guid":"GwrgsaSa5KPBKWWTOSETGQ","children":[{"id":"74","parent":"73","text":"• Diarrea crónica, intermitente o persistente.","guid":"670WaCQ1Cg4T-c0njWA8zw","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"73","text":"• Esteatorrea, distensión abdominal, pérdida de peso, déficit de minerales y vitaminas liposolubles.","guid":"XSdI75YBRfPDzfWAi8ucNQ","children":[]},{"id":"76","parent":"73","text":"• Infecciones GI.","guid":"KLv5JJpHg1ulHnKn33gABA","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"73","text":"• Enteropatía autoinmune (AIE).","guid":"xBUU5O_t0d1dw0XozU54KA","children":[]},{"id":"78","parent":"73","text":"• Granulomas.","guid":"DqxBVKR92vF0_PLQ-WDgJQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"79","parent":"63","text":"• Afectación\\Nhepática:","guid":"jKFuLbL-ZybGEJ0727nP-g","children":[{"id":"80","parent":"79","text":"• Al menos 10% de los pacientes.","guid":"myCTphARxhwX3gOxfgyQgQ","children":[]},{"id":"81","parent":"79","text":"• Causas: infecciones, reacciones autoinmunes, linfoproliferación y neoplasias, granulomas, infiltración de células inflamatorias, obstrucción biliar intrahepática.","guid":"xGuIqn90tO9wx67MbHbj-w","children":[]},{"id":"82","parent":"79","text":"• Asociación fuerte con enteropatía linfocítica.","guid":"wTE1Na3O-QGTm3dL6JGhsg","children":[]},{"id":"83","parent":"79","text":"• Papel patogénico del eje intestino-hígado.","guid":"faJJDibGwVcdovdaN_J--A","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"84","parent":"42","text":"Inmunodeficiencia\\NAdquirida","guid":"4ZdXO7KjqeoAeFDbk2LGCQ","children":[{"id":"85","parent":"84","text":"Infecciones en Pacientes\\NInmunosuprimidos","guid":"Hb0kwOliYU6vTn9kOixwOA","children":[{"id":"86","parent":"85","text":"• Contexto: Uso de inmunosupresores, terapias oncológicas, corticosteroides, terapias biológicas.","guid":"6IfTZ-z7yNUyIhTmHyoW0A","children":[]},{"id":"87","parent":"85","text":"• Riesgo: ↑Morbilidad, potencialmente letales.","guid":"xHpb4wpC_d_ROK-VBLSLPw","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"85","text":"• Revisión sistemática\\N(Stuck et al., 2016):","guid":"","children":[{"id":"89","parent":"88","text":"• RR: 1,6 (IC 95% 1,3-1,9).","guid":"mSrgt952-lG8lTqOqUj4CA","children":[]},{"id":"90","parent":"88","text":"• Dosis de corticoides ≤ 30 mg/día de prednisona: 9-58 eventos\\Ninfecciosos/100 pacientes/año, ↑ en EII vs. patologías reumatológicas.","guid":"PVjngLFaanAHN9cbQke8mA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"91","parent":"84","text":"Fármacos","guid":"O0_rHiPxGG76Zb2MbV6YXg","children":[{"id":"92","parent":"91","text":"• Corticoides:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"93","parent":"92","text":"• Frecuencia: Infecciones más comunes.","guid":"OrBGlMOCKwRcOs7bt6LiDw","children":[]},{"id":"94","parent":"92","text":"• Manifestaciones digestivas: Dependientes de dosis, tiempo de uso, comorbilidades.","guid":"QT014I5-M5f5fxlaEKWbKw","children":[]},{"id":"95","parent":"92","text":"• Patógenos frecuentes: Candida albicans (colonización orofaríngea, esofágica).","guid":"09XzjXxErSrdp6C8dxb5cA","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"96","parent":"42","text":"Patógenos\\NComunes (Tabla\\N2)","guid":"k_iW9LxCLCvbbj8yMznJkg","children":[{"id":"97","parent":"96","text":"• Bacterias:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"98","parent":"97","text":"• Enterobacterias: ITU, bacteriemias.","guid":"zOac-x7pwp_pDEeYeZ0mRg","children":[]},{"id":"99","parent":"97","text":"• Staphylococcus aureus: Bacteriemias, infecciones de piel y tejidos blandos.","guid":"A4Cgu-1_xoXj7VqzHlBBEA","children":[]},{"id":"100","parent":"97","text":"• Streptococcus spp.: Bacteriemias, infecciones de piel y tejidos blandos.","guid":"-RfN4YaTlJwojyF6ZYjiFA","children":[]},{"id":"101","parent":"97","text":"• Salmonella spp.: Diarrea, bacteriemia.","guid":"kIP8vQJ38Q_UrnhCgh2ghQ","children":[]},{"id":"102","parent":"97","text":"• Legionella: Neumonía.","guid":"YWKRtHyLUjUeqn4IqRYyIg","children":[]},{"id":"103","parent":"97","text":"• Listeria monocytogenes: Bacteriemia, meningitis, romboencefalitis.","guid":"bqW_cwPug13ofa0i0bbbWQ","children":[]},{"id":"104","parent":"97","text":"• Nocardia sp.: Neumonía, abscesos cerebrales y cutáneos.","guid":"S49Bd6E1S26U7Y6-OtjLaA","children":[]},{"id":"105","parent":"97","text":"• Rhodococcus equi: Neumonía, abscesos, bacteriemia.","guid":"8xn9MnFWE23_Xp0v4A_tQg","children":[]},{"id":"106","parent":"97","text":"• Mycobacterium tuberculosis: Tuberculosis.","guid":"McUEHiaV4VnX9uF8QMjR8A","children":[]},{"id":"107","parent":"97","text":"• Clostridium difficile: Diarrea, colitis pseudomembranosa.","guid":"zPJ_BME4YAFc0VoQ1qk2Fg","children":[]}]},{"id":"108","parent":"96","text":"• Virus:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"109","parent":"108","text":"• Virus respiratorios: Neumonía.","guid":"ow8Y_bMSh108c0PADkfnvQ","children":[]},{"id":"110","parent":"108","text":"• Citomegalovirus: Compromiso digestivo, pulmonar, SNC.","guid":"qv2Te4GikyhbZ-L3BNLPtg","children":[]},{"id":"111","parent":"108","text":"• Herpes simplex: Infecciones diseminadas, crónicas, hepatitis.","guid":"PhQGYP8F5UOwnPn71_NFiQ","children":[]},{"id":"112","parent":"108","text":"• Varicela zoster: Herpes zóster, varicela diseminada.","guid":"k9ZPUe5_SV1XAXdnY6BHkA","children":[]},{"id":"113","parent":"108","text":"• Parvovirus B19: Pancitopenia, síntomas lúpicos.","guid":"UBJRCeYIAqgb3P9j1Ue_3w","children":[]},{"id":"114","parent":"108","text":"• Virus hepatitis B: Riesgo de reactivación.","guid":"B06cK40Ae1r4f7YCYuISmg","children":[]}]},{"id":"115","parent":"96","text":"• Hongos:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"116","parent":"115","text":"• Candida spp.: Candidiasis cutánea, mucosa, sistémica.","guid":"BvPJMERidMOR15O_vXELcg","children":[]},{"id":"117","parent":"115","text":"• Cryptococcus sp.: SNC, pulmonar.","guid":"U0kDjYx2IBxV25oRJqIRjg","children":[]},{"id":"118","parent":"115","text":"• Pneumocystis jiroveci: Neumonía.","guid":"XqhRtXE8S7-_kyHUwbyR3w","children":[]},{"id":"119","parent":"115","text":"• Aspergillus spp.: Aspergilosis pulmonar invasora.","guid":"lHWCUzvHml46NjPDiUr2Mg","children":[]},{"id":"120","parent":"115","text":"• Zygomycetes: Mucormicosis rino craneofacial, pulmonar.","guid":"YpgE9mVBAsTaR1-XJ9J-bg","children":[]}]},{"id":"121","parent":"96","text":"• Parásitos:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"122","parent":"121","text":"• Toxoplasma gondii: Toxoplasmosis (SNC, coriorretinitis, neumonía).","guid":"L3tOZzlJW4iPJOx0FCZnhw","children":[]}]},{"id":"123","parent":"96","text":"• Protozoos intestinales: Cryptosporidium\\Nsp., Giardia intestinalis, Entamoeba\\Nhistolytica (diarrea, disentería).","guid":"yP1MjkeL30DFTtjhUkZRXg","children":[]},{"id":"124","parent":"96","text":"• Nematodes: Strongyloides sp.\\N(compromiso intestinal, hiperinfestación).","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"125","parent":"0","text":"Infecciones en\\NPacientes con\\NVIH-SIDA","guid":"","children":[{"id":"126","parent":"125","text":"• Prevalencia: 71 mil\\Npersonas en Chile (2017).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"127","parent":"125","text":"• Autopsias: 82% con lesiones\\Ndigestivas, 38% con más de\\Nun sitio afectado.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"128","parent":"125","text":"• Principios diagnósticos:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"129","parent":"125","text":"• Síntomas y signos clínicos: Rara vez\\Ndiagnósticos por sí solos.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"130","parent":"125","text":"• Maniobras no\\Ninvasivas: Preferidas.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"131","parent":"125","text":"• Infecciones\\Nmúltiples:\\NFrecuentes.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"132","parent":"125","text":"• Diagnóstico predictivo: Basado en\\Ngrado de inmunocompromiso.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"133","parent":"125","text":"• Manifestaciones GI tardías:\\NParte de infecciones\\Nsistémicas (CMV, M. avium).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"134","parent":"125","text":"• Neoplasias digestivas: Linfomas,\\Nsarcoma de Kaposi, carcinoma anal.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"135","parent":"0","text":"Manifestaciones\\NClínicas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"136","parent":"0","text":"Neumonía","guid":"","children":[{"id":"137","parent":"136","text":"• Agentes: Staphylococcus aureus,\\NLegionella, Pneumocystis jirovecii","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"138","parent":"136","text":"• Manifestaciones:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"139","parent":"136","text":"• Bacteriemia, infecciones del SNC,\\Nartritis (Staphylococcus aureus).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"140","parent":"136","text":"• Neumonía, cuadros diseminados\\N(Legionella, Pneumocystis jirovecii).","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"141","parent":"0","text":"Diarrea","guid":"","children":[{"id":"142","parent":"141","text":"• Agentes: Enterobacterias, Salmonella\\Nspp., Clostridium difficile, Cryptosporidium\\Nsp., Giardia intestinalis.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"143","parent":"141","text":"• Manifestaciones:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"144","parent":"141","text":"• Diarrea asociada\\Na antibióticos.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"145","parent":"141","text":"• Enteropatía\\Nidiopática a HIV.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"146","parent":"141","text":"• Diarrea inducida por drogas\\N(azatioprina, quimioterapias,\\Nciclosporina A, metotrexato).","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"147","parent":"0","text":"Herpes Zoster (HZ)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"148","parent":"147","text":"• Agente: Virus de la\\Nvaricela-zoster (VZV).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"149","parent":"147","text":"• Manifestaciones:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"150","parent":"147","text":"• HZ diseminado.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"151","parent":"147","text":"• HZ oftálmico.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"152","parent":"0","text":"Reactivación\\Nde Hepatitis","guid":"","children":[{"id":"153","parent":"152","text":"• Agente: Virus de la\\Nhepatitis B (VHB).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"154","parent":"152","text":"• Manifestaciones:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"155","parent":"152","text":"• Reactivación al retirar\\Nterapia inmunosupresora.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"156","parent":"0","text":"Infecciones Fúngicas","guid":"","children":[{"id":"157","parent":"156","text":"• Agentes: Candida spp., Cryptococcus sp.,\\NAspergillus spp., Zygomycetes.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"158","parent":"156","text":"• Manifestaciones:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"159","parent":"156","text":"• Candidiasis de piel,\\Nmucosas, sistémica.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"160","parent":"156","text":"• Neumonía, aspergilosis\\Npulmonar invasora.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"161","parent":"156","text":"• Mucormicosis rino\\Ncraneofacial o pulmonar.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"162","parent":"0","text":"Infecciones en Pacientes\\NInmunocomprometidos (por VIH/SIDA)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"163","parent":"0","text":"Diagnóstico y\\NTratamiento (Tablas 5 y\